 no one had witnessed but one man and one woman. Umar said, \u201cThis is a secret marriage and I do not permit it. If I had known of it beforehand, I would\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32780,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/13\/umar-riddah-murtad-silm\/","url_meta":{"origin":15417,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Apostasy: Apostates return peacefully or imprisoned","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: I said, \u201cO commander of the faithful, some people have turned renegade against Islam and joined the idolaters. What is to be done other than killing them?\u201d Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThat I take hold of them on peaceful terms\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14477,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/31\/ibn-kab-salaam-non-muslims\/","url_meta":{"origin":15417,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Ka\u2019b on Salaam: No harm greeting non-Muslims with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 31, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Ka\u2019b reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked about initiating the greeting of peace to non-Muslim citizens and he said we should respond to their greeting, but we do not greet them first. As for me, I do not see any harm\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u